text: Dagmawit Moges Bekele (; born 10 December 1983) is an Ethiopian politician serving as the current Minister of Transport of the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia since October 2018. She has served also as Deputy Mayor and Communication Affairs Bureau Head of Addis Ababa City Administration.
